{"tid":2507552,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"食肆拒為錢屈從：人命嚟","createTime":"2021-04-28T05:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T05:40:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1012147c954a88a5392364672fc53c7646ad84ac","tid":2507552,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T05:28:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210428/B7KUWYOKVZDQRAWF4CW636EZSU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210428%2FB7KUWYOKVZDQRAWF4CW636EZSU%2F&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0mZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=905476e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210428%2FB7KUWYOKVZDQRAWF4CW636EZSU%2F&h=38e8016c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210428/B7KUWYOKVZDQRAWF4CW636EZSU/</a><br />\n<br />\n食肆拒為錢屈從：人命嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tbanp8y5oL6nk0WTjbok2DMOTCI=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GYHD7QEAIVCTNAVZ7NDRE7VRHQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ftbanp8y5oL6nk0WTjbok2DMOTCI%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGYHD7QEAIVCTNAVZ7NDRE7VRHQ.jpg&h=a5ae73c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黃傑龍指會與員工商討疫苗氣泡計劃。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府以放寬晚市營業時間及入座人數作利誘，鼓勵食肆強迫員工注射疫苗。不過有食肆負責人認為，接種疫苗屬個人選擇，人命關天，難為員工因打針致死負責，寧願維持現狀，不願為增加營業額而冒險。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：社會信用系統殺到  食肆分四級 打針有特權 虛報罰五千<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃店藍店同樣不滿<br />\n<br />\n消夜時段屬甜品店重要收入來源，不過，尖沙嘴一家甜品店主管馬先生表示，與老闆商討後，寧願忍痛放棄營業額，亦不會強迫員工打針，大嘆新措施「嘥氣」，並怒斥政府做法矯枉過正，「不嬲都話病毒唔係夜晚先出嚟，如果要打，咁點解唔係你一入餐廳就要打針？」政府容許食肆劃分區域接待打針及不打針食客，他認為政府只着眼大財團，「我哋咁細間，點劃分個區域出嚟呀？再細啲根本冇可能做到。」<br />\n<br />\n黃店「桔梗」負責人Ivan曾詢問員工意願，均表示因擔心副作用，不欲接種疫苗，故決定維持堂食至晚上10時。他認為政府做法荒謬，「人命嚟，唔可能叫佢哋拎條命出嚟返工，患病都可能會好得返，但打（疫苗）係有機會即刻死。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：蒲吧唱K須打針 竹館豁免  醫生：打麻雀長時間逗留兼換枱易播毒<br />\n<br />\n同是黃店的「開餐Dine Inn」老闆Eddy亦表示，放寬數小時對生意幫助不大。Joyful Dessert House負責人更得悉附近有「藍店」員工知道有關消息亦感不滿，因他們年紀較大，擔心接種後不幸死亡。<br />\n<br />\n食肆員工須醫生證明方可豁免打針，叙福樓集團主席的黃傑龍表示，對有關安排感「頭赤」，需與員工詳細討論，「我上兩個星期講過唔可以逼員工打針，呢點係唔會變」，旗下食肆會維持營業至晚上10時，「要有足夠時間、同事商量，大家想唔想參加，先至知道有冇資格參加（疫苗氣泡），如果好多同事唔想參加，咁我都冇資格參加。」"},{"pid":"6e76b103956151f0caa31151af6654c858aa467b","tid":2507552,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T05:33:50.000Z","msg":"有良心"},{"pid":"1657239abb9d863a5737712a2426a38efd876354","tid":2507552,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T05:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d00f380625f4dccfc832946fd8b504315aa3553","tid":2507552,"uid":127033,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T05:36:48.000Z","msg":"桔梗呢間野唔係伏撚到仆街咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c225e35c1076a23ead04d18f07ca48b17364b3","tid":2507552,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T05:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}